@fkunpadfair is a series of events that's held biennially. After holding the previous events (Bioscope, Pasific Fest and Megabaksos), FK Unpad Fair will celebrate the success by holding a charity concert for people with Lupus.
.
I, Samuel Saragih, realize that awareness of lupus is still low. But by doing this campaign, I know that Kidney Disorder is one of the characteristics of Lupus.
.
So let's spread the word and support FK UNPAD FAIR 2016!
.
Sasana Budaya Ganesha Bandung
December 3rd, 2016.
Be there, let's celebrate!
